data.description: Opportunity is knocking! Spacious 6 Bed 2 Bath classic Colonial in thriving Elizabeth is more than meets the eye! Bursting with possibilities, just awaiting your personal touch, this home has good bones and a spacious layout with 2000+ sq ft of finished living. The main level features a tiled Foyer entry that opens to a light and bright Living room with hardwood floors that flow seamlessly into the large Formal Dining room. Sizable Eat-in-Kitchen offers granite counters, ceramic flooring, backsplash and ample cabinet storage. Updated Full Bath off the dining room adds to the convenience. Upstairs, the 2nd updated Full Bath, along with 3 generous Bedrooms. Finished third level holds 3 more versatile Bedrooms that can double as a Home Office, Den, etc. Sump pump has been installed in the walk-out basement, finish it off for even more living space! Rear deck and stairs recently redone, with a fenced-in Backyard that is your blank canvas. Addtl features inc newer front outdoor steps, a front fenced yard, and recently repaired Roof (2 years). All in a prime commuter location, just a half mile to both North and Elizabeth NJ Transit stations, easy access to Rte 9, close to shopping, dining and more! Don't miss out! This could be the hidden gem you've been searching for! *Showings begin Sunday 4/14*
